{"3324350": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "攻城略地搶人妻", "steam_appid": 3324350, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主公！組好你的手牌，擊敗各路勢力（搶人妻），成為三國霸主！這就是你的使命啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遊戲中，你將根據手中的卡牌組成特定牌型打出，對敵人造成傷害！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擊敗敵人後，他們就能被你收為部下（後宮）啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>爆衣系統</strong><br>每位角色都搭載了爆衣系統，在遊戲過程中，角色會隨著關卡推進，切換到 <strong>爆衣1階段</strong> 和 <strong>爆衣2階段</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下方是部分角色的爆衣展示效果圖：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/013a32430f82789aedb86f3b4bdccab3.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=649 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/013a32430f82789aedb86f3b4bdccab3.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/0afdca41fc704f452213de131610ce8e.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=649 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/0afdca41fc704f452213de131610ce8e.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/4cfa3882804c87314c47c6503439832d.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=649 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/4cfa3882804c